Installed ok but some of the vc textures don't appear correctly nor does the galley. Tried installing different ways but can't sort it. Still a great plane though. Thanks

To correct the interior texture problem you need to take some of the texture files from the Boeing_737_900ER_FSX and add them to the aircraft you want to correct. These are the files you need to replace:
1) Replace all B737ng_vc files
2) Replace B737ng_gauges file
3) Replace B737ng_gauges_I
4) Add B737ng_interior_material_t
If you want the Flight Attendant view you need to copy the CameraDefinition 003 from the Boeing_737_900ER_FSX to the aircraft you want. Hope this helps.
